55
00:03:37,412 --> 00:03:39,311
I told you not to be intimidated by others, not to beat them up.

56
00:03:39,612 --> 00:03:41,751
They started it first.

57
00:03:42,051 --> 00:03:44,981
He's right. They started it.

58
00:03:44,982 --> 00:03:46,520
That's right. Ho Woo didn't do anything wrong.

59
00:03:46,521 --> 00:03:47,822
See?

60
00:03:47,952 --> 00:03:50,091
Forget it. Let's go eat.

61
00:03:50,692 --> 00:03:52,591
Look at him getting away so easily...

62
00:03:53,561 --> 00:03:54,831
