110
00:06:07,022 --> 00:06:09,491
Ho Woo.

111
00:06:09,592 --> 00:06:10,691
Coming.

112
00:06:13,462 --> 00:06:14,501
All right.

113
00:06:17,402 --> 00:06:18,542
Welcome.

114
00:06:20,272 --> 00:06:23,141
